data.description: Welcome to 3409 Ripple Road, a charming and updated home in the heart of Windsor Mill. Step inside and be greeted by high quality vinyl flooring in the spacious living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing after a long day. The bedrooms feature soft, plush carpets for a cozy and comfortable feel. The updated kitchen boasts extra storage space and is perfect for the aspiring chef. With a garage, driveway, and street parking, you'll never have to worry about finding a spot for your vehicles. Plus, the property comes equipped with a solar system, saving you money on energy bills.   Enjoy the outdoors in the generous sized yard, perfect for summer events, and relax on the rear patio or front porch. The central location provides easy access to BWI Airport, local dining, multiple shopping centers, and entertainment venues.   Additional features include a storage shed, finished basement, washer and dryer with a convenient laundry chute, and a master bathroom with a lifetime warranty. HVAC replaced in December, 2022 while the roof was replaced in 2018. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a beautiful home in a prime location. Schedule your showing today!
